login name                              anonymous
password                                user@example.com

list supported commands                 help
print help about given command          help ‹cmd›

print CWD on remote machine             pwd
print CWD on local machine              lpwd

change CWD on remote machine            cd ‹dir›
# on most  anonymous FTP  servers, the  files for  public downloading  are found
# somewhere under the `pub/` directory

change CWD on local machine             lcd ‹dir›

list directory on remote machine        ls

download file from remote               get ‹file›
# on the local machine, the file will be downloaded into `lpwd`

log off the remote                      bye
